## Requirements

### Must Have (Phase 1 - MVP)

**1. Canvas Foundation**
- Infinite pan/zoom canvas (like Figma/Miro)
- Grid with snap-to-grid option
- Smooth pan (drag background)
- Zoom (mouse wheel, pinch, buttons)
- Multi-select (drag box, shift-click)
- Copy/paste, undo/redo

**2. Shape Primitives**
- Rectangle, Rounded Rectangle
- Circle, Ellipse
- Triangle, Diamond
- Line, Arrow (single/double head)
- Freehand pen (smooth curves)
- Text boxes (editable in-place)

**3. Shape Properties**
- Fill color (transparent option)
- Stroke color, width, style (solid, dashed, dotted)
- Corner radius (for rectangles)
- Font size, family, weight (for text)
- Rotation
- Z-index (bring to front/back)

**4. Connector System**
- Smart connectors (auto-attach to shapes)
- Straight, curved, orthogonal (right-angle) connectors
- Arrow heads (start, end, both, none)
