**8. UI/UX**
- Toolbar: Tools (select, shapes, pen, text, connector)
- Properties panel: Color pickers, stroke width, etc.
- Layers panel: Z-order management
- Page structure: Library (/diagrams), Editor (/diagrams/:id)
- Dark mode support

