## Performance Considerations

**Bundle Size:**
- **Zero external diagram libraries** - All custom code
- Estimated: ~30-50KB for all diagram code (gzipped)
- Lazy-loaded: No initial bundle impact
- **Total Impact**: Minimal, all our own code

**Runtime Performance:**
- SVG for shapes: Scales to ~500 elements smoothly
- Canvas for freehand: Hardware accelerated
- Debounced auto-save (2s)
- IndexedDB persistence (non-blocking)
- Optimizations: Virtual rendering for 1000+ elements (Phase 3)

**Export Performance:**
- PNG: SVG to canvas via foreignObject (~100ms)
- SVG: Direct serialization (<50ms)
- PDF: jsPDF generation (~200ms)

